  <h3>Product Overview</h3>
  <p>The <strong>Ultra-High Barrier Transparent PET-AlOx Film (Retortable) - PET-AlOx-DTZ</strong> is engineered to meet the highest industry standards for flexible packaging and functional applications. Utilizing advanced manufacturing processes, this material delivers exceptional performance tailored for specialized needs.</p>
  
  <h3>Key Characteristics</h3>
  <ul>
