  <h3>Product Overview</h3>
  <p>The <strong>High-Gloss Metallized PET Film - VMPET-GL</strong> is engineered to meet the highest industry standards for flexible packaging and functional applications. Utilizing advanced manufacturing processes, this material delivers exceptional performance tailored for specialized needs.</p>
  
  <h3>Key Characteristics</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Core Advantage:</strong> Mirror Effect</li>
    <li><strong>Application:</strong> High Reflectivity</li>
    <li><strong>Original Spec:</strong> 聚酯高亮镀铝膜 VMPET-GL</li>
    <li><strong>Quality Assurance:</strong> Manufactured with precision to ensure uniform thickness, excellent barrier properties, and superior mechanical strength.</li>
